// ✅ Triggers: 5 defined (choice, 2 VFX, entry dialogue, exit transition)
// ✅ Anchors: 3 conduits at 120° intervals (spec-accurate positions)
// ⏳ Navigation Mesh: Placeholder, pending generation
// ✅ Dialogue Nodes: 4 defined (arrival, choice, 2 branch commentaries)
// ✅ Cinematic Triggers: 1 defined (crossroads_reveal)
// ✅ Decision Prompts: 1 defined (storm_routing with 2 options)
